+   * @param   stack BeanShell call stack.
+   * @return  True if succeeds.
+   * @since   0.0.1
+   */
+  public static String invoke(Interpreter i, CallStack stack) {
+    GrouperShell.setOurCommand(i, true);
+    return invoke(null);
+  }
+

+   * <p/>
